# {{app_name}} API

## Overview

This is a [FastAPI](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/) application for document processing using AWS Bedrock Data Automation. It includes:

- Document upload and processing via AWS Bedrock Data Automation
- Asynchronous processing with status tracking via DynamoDB
- Metrics collection and aggregation (daily/monthly) stored in S3
- RESTful API with automatic OpenAPI documentation
- Lambda functions for background processing
- Integration with AWS services (S3, DynamoDB, SQS, Athena, Bedrock Data Automation, EventBridge)

