### рџ› пёЏ Development

#### API Documentation

- Swagger UI: http://localhost:8000/docs
- ReDoc: http://localhost:8000/redoc

#### Key Endpoints

Document Processing:
- `POST /v1/documents/upload` - Upload a document for processing
- `GET /v1/documents/{document_id}` - Get document status and results

Schemas:
- `GET /v1/schemas` - List all supported document types
- `GET /v1/schemas/{document_type}` - Get field schema for a document type

Metrics:
- `GET /v1/metrics` - Get aggregated metrics with daily or monthly granularity

    ```bash
    # Daily metrics for a single date
    GET /v1/metrics?start_date=2024-02-25&granularity=daily

    # Daily metrics for a date range
    GET /v1/metrics?start_date=2024-02-01&end_date=2024-02-28&granularity=daily

    # Monthly metrics
    GET /v1/metrics?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-03-31&granularity=monthly
    ```

    _Parameters:_
    - `start_date` (required): Start date in YYYY-MM-DD format
    - `end_date` (optional): End date in YYYY-MM-DD format (defaults to start_date)
    - `granularity` (optional): `daily` or `monthly` (defaults to `daily`)

    _Response includes:_
    - Total records processed
    - Processing status breakdown
    - Document classification counts
    - Response code distribution
    - Timing statistics (processing time, BDA wait time)

